mment_count": 13, "comments": [{"author": "cas.7857", "author_id": "45648753801", "id": "17875548417520091", "text": "Thank you! Every word is true for me.  I'm  rebellious since childhood  cause I realized the lies anyway, but I was not strong enough to resist or to keep me out of this game. Not to be  programmed anyway was impossible. Now I'm awakening and much stronger.  But It feels to bekomme fucking insane twice. First, when I was an angry, fearful child feeling alone and misunderstood. Now I follow my heart,  I'm more  who I really am, much resistant than ever. But it hurts so much to recognize  that  the world is more evel and satanic than I could ever imagine.", "timestamp": 1772391864}, {"author": "murrayelizabethd", "author_id": "12434172204", "id": "18096966134491513", "text": "🙏🏼🕉🙏🏼👑👑👑🏡🔥", "timestamp": 1771792421}, {"author": "mandywattam", "author_id": "8296551022", "id": "17887381299328215", "text": "Too true", "timestamp": 1771773847}, {"author": "lisitsky_film", "author_id": "43874842327", "id": "18166871596398448", "text": "This world is been designed to experience that what we are not on the other side! There we are gods! And yes this world is a game that we play, a free will experiment that got to distorted with time. And yes it is run on fear now…", "timestamp": 1771674108}, {"author": "_faroles", "author_id": "863237443", "id": "17848569033646109", "text": "🔥🔥🔥", "timestamp": 1771294998}, {"author": "goldschmiede_sinnenwerkstatt", "author_id": "5806844574", "id": "18309856042284437", "text": "Absolutely❤️", "timestamp": 1771292067}, {"author": "nutrition.junkie", "author_id": "6206585155", "id": "17941682142155606", "text": "Every word of it 👏👏👏", "timestamp": 1771276187}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/625031127_1399807774470607_3166965114433130762_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz